Instance of a governing process model that controls the maturity state of a Project Planning object (enterprise project, task, milestone, or gate). This field gets auto-populated when the governing process model is started.
E6WCommonApps.Label.Tooltip.ProjectMatur:
The maturity state of the project which can be:

  • Draft: Assigned tasks do not show up in the Collaborative Tasks app for the assignees when the project is in the Draft maturity state. Only the Owner and Leader can edit.
  • To Do: Project is ready for planning. The Owner, Leader and Author can edit.
  • In Work: Project is started and a work in progress. The Owner, Leader, Author and Assignee can edit.
  • On Hold: Project is on Hold. Only the Owner and Leader can edit. Assigned tasks do not show up in the Collaborative Tasks app for the assignees when the project is in the Hold maturity state.
  • Completed: Project is completed regardless of the maturity state of its tasks, milestones, and gates.
E6WCommonApps.Label.Tooltip.ProjectTempl:
The maturity state of the project template which can be:

  • Draft: Initial maturity state of the project template.
  • Published: The template is finalized and ready for use to create projects from the template.
E6WCommonApps.Label.Tooltip.TaskMaturity:
The maturity state of the task which can be:

  • To Do: The task is created but not started.
  • In Work: The task is started and a work in progress.
  • Completed: The task is finished.
E6WCommonApps.Label.Tooltip.MilestoneMat:
The maturity state of the milestone which can be:

  • To Do: The milestone is about to start.
  • In Work: The milestone is in progress.
  • Completed: The milestone is achieved.
E6WCommonApps.Label.Tooltip.GateMaturity:
The maturity state of the gate which can be:

  • To Do: The gate is about to start.
  • In Work: The gate is in progress.
  • Completed: The gate is achieved.

E6WCommonApps.Label.Tooltip.StartDateCon:
Conditions for when this task starts:

  • None: No specific constraints set to the task.
  • Fixed: The task must start on this particular date.
    • {CONSTRAINTS}

• No later than: The task is scheduled to start on or before the selected date.
  • No earlier than: The task is scheduled to start on or after the selected date.
E6WCommonApps.Label.Tooltip.SuggestedDat:
• None: No specific constraints are set for the gate or milestone.
  • Fixed: The gate or milestone is fixed and cannot be changed by the scheduler.
  • No later than: The gate or milestone date cannot be set later than this date.
  • No earlier than: The gate or milestone date cannot be set earlier than this date.
E6WCommonApps.Label.Tooltip.EndDateConst:
Conditions for when this task ends:

  • None: No specific constraints set to the task.
  • Fixed: The task must end on this particular date.
    • {CONSTRAINTS}

• No later than: The task is scheduled to start on or before the selected date.
  • No earlier than: The task is scheduled to start on or after the selected date.
